product_name: BlueWater 5.5mm Titan Dyneema Accessory Cord - Package of 20 ft.
long_description: Ideal for slinging chocks, nuts and other pro, BlueWater 5.5mm Titan Dyneema accessory cord combines high strength, low elongation and light weight. Titan Dyneema offers greater abrasion and cut resistance than nylon. When tying loops, it's recommended to use a triple fisherman's knot.
